---
title: Satay Chicken & Zesty Rice with Cucumber Salad & Lime
description: Here’s a dish for all the peanut butter lovers out there. Silky chicken meets creamy, nutty satay sauce in this flavour-packed meal. Paired with zesty rice and a refreshing cucumber salad, it’s a vibrant, plant-based delight that hits all the right notes.

